BEFORE THE RIGHT HON.
BENJAMIN SAMUEL PHILLIPS, LORD MAYOR of the City of London; The Hon. Sir
JAMES SHAW WILLES , Knt., one of the Justices of Her Majesty's Court of Common Pleas; Sir
WILLIAM SHEE , Knt., one of the Justices of Her Majesty's Court of Queen's Bench; Sir
FRANCIS GRAHAM MOON , Bart, F.S.A.;
JOHN CARTER , Esq., F.A.S., and F.R.A.S.;
THOMAS GABRIEL , Esq.; WILLIAM FERNELEY ALLEN, Esq.;
THOMAS DAKIN , Esq., and
DAVID STONE , Esq., Aldermen of the said City;
THOMAS CHAMBERS , Esq., Q.C., M.P., Common Serjeant of the said City; and
ROBERT MALCOLM KERR , Esq., Judge of the Sheriffs' Court; Her Majesty's Justices of Oyer and Terminer and General Goal Delivery of Newgate, holden for the said City, and Judges of the Central Criminal Court.
